data.name: Thaddaeus, the Ultramafic
data.notes: "Thaddaeus, the Ultramafic" burrows up out of the ground between Lake Ciel and Cleansing Spring in south easy Sylvalum. As with other Cinicula it has a lot of HP and strong defences but while it isn't too dangerous by itself it lives in the path of a wandering Xe-Dom making a prolonged fight potentially dangerous.
